      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARJAYBRO (9) started from a wide draw on the second line last start. Went forward to settle handy then boxed on gamely and finished 3.5 metres from the winner in third at Junee over 1760m. Hard to know where he gets from this slightly awkward draw. Meets a comparable field and he is capable of taking this out. BAYRIDGE TOMMY (1) has been racing well of late. Finished third at his latest appearance over 1758m at Leeton, beaten 6 metres. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Leading hope based on recent form. JUSTAQUICKSCHOONER (5) was responsible for a better effort last time out when third over 1720m at Young. Should run a big race. THE HEATS ON LEXY (7) could only finish eighth over 1760m at Junee most recently. Open to improvement and is in the mix.",
